  = link_to "benefits of argan oil,", "http://skabuorganics.com/articles/10-proven-benefits-moroccan-argan-oil-shampoo/"
  so this is a recap. Argan oil is high in essential fatty acids that reduce aging, and protects against environmental damage caused by UV radiation. It also repairs split ends by coating the hair shaft, which reduces breakage and drying.

%h2 2. Never Use a Shampoo With Sulfates Or Parabens
%p
  Sulfates have been linked to cancer and to eye damage, which are things that will undoubtedly make you look older. Parabens have been linked to breast cancer. If you want to live longer and look younger, sulfates and parabens are best to be avoided.

